Open Dashboard Response Class

Source: R/open_dashboard.R
OpenResp.Rd

Open Dashboard Response Class

Usage

openRespDash(response = list())

open_dashboard()

Arguments

response

<list> or <openRespDash> object returned from the API call to the dashboard.

Value

An S7 <openRespDash> object.

Examples

open_dashboard()
#> <openRespDash>
